John Levene https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Levene 0 John Levene (born John Anthony Woods, 24 December 1941) is an English actor. His best-known role was that of Corporal, Sergeant, and later Warrant Officer, John Benton, of the UNIT in the science-fiction television series Doctor Who.
